723298f-a.text:
South Street, under the Brooklyn Bridge, showing several warehouses that face the East River, and from which the photoErapher is viewing. These bear No's. 168-70 South Street. They
are between Dover and Foosevelt Street's.
Ootober 1927
George L. Balgue, photo

May 3, 1932.
